## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-102"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> 是在 System.Speech 实现语义技术的主对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-102"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> is the primary object that implements the semantic technology in System.Speech.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="89500-103">语义解释允许可由一个识别引擎来正确解释音频输入定义规则使用的语法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-103">Semantic interpretation allows grammars to define rules for use by a recognition engine to correctly interpret audio input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="89500-104">语义解释还允许识别引擎来组织其结果，以便它们可以更轻松地处理，而不是仅返回识别的单词和单词的序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-104">Semantic interpretation also enables recognition engines to organize their results so that they can be more easily processed, rather than returning only recognized words and sequences of words.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-105">例如，识别引擎输出"将背景更改为红色"必须进行分析和解释应用程序，它无法得到处理之前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-105">For example, the recognition engine output "Change background to red" would have to be parsed and interpreted by an application before it could be acted upon.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="89500-106">A<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象可以指定要通过指定短语具有两个语义子结构，一个用于选择背景或前景 （文本所表示的"后台"），和另一个用于选择更清楚处理语义解释（由文本"red"） 的颜色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-106">A <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object can specify a semantic interpretation to make processing clearer by specifying that the phrase has two semantic substructures, one for selecting background or foreground (represented by the text "background"), and the other for selecting color (represented by the text "red").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-107">System.Speech 表示识别操作的树中的语义<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-107">System.Speech represents the semantics of a recognition operation in a tree of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-108">每个<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例包括以下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-108">Each <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance includes the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="89500-109"><xref:System.Object>、 通过访问<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A>属性，用于密钥的实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-109">An <xref:System.Object>, accessed by means of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property, used to key the instance of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="89500-110">语义分析的准确性的度量值返回<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-110">A measure of the accuracy of semantic parsing, returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="89500-111">名称/值对的集合 (<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>) 的子对象，这两项也<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-111">A collection of name/value pairs (<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>) of child objects, which are also <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="89500-112">子节点都可通过访问<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实现<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>使用字符串查找键和一个<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例，如以下示例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-112">Child nodes are accessible through the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> implementation of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> using a string lookup key and a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance, as in the following example.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    foreach (KeyValuePair<String, SemanticValue> child in semantics)   
    {  
      Utils.CreateSemanticsTreeNodes(semanticsNode.Nodes, child.Value, child.Key);  
    }  
    ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-113">提供有效的实例时识别引擎基于 System.Speech<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>从识别的所有输出，即使是对于短语与没有显式的语义结构。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-113">Recognition engines based on System.Speech provide valid instances of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> for all output from recognition, even for phrases with no explicit semantic structure.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-114"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例使用获取短语<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A>属性<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase>对象 (或多个对象从它继承，如<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance for a phrase is obtained using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> object (or objects that inherit from it, such as <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> 获取识别的短语没有语义的结构的对象的特征是：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> objects obtained for recognized phrases without semantic structure are characterized by:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="89500-116">在缺乏子级 (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Count%2A>为 0)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-116">The lack of children (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Count%2A> is 0).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="89500-117"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> 属性为 `null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property is `null`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="89500-118">1.0 人工语义置信度 (返回<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-118">An artificial semantic confidence level of 1.0 (returned by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-119">通常，应用程序创建<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>间接，实例将它们添加到<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>情况下的，结合<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-119">Typically, applications create <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instances indirectly, adding them to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> objects by using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> instances,  in conjunction with  <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="89500-120">直接构造<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例的强类型的语法创建过程中很有用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="89500-120">Direct construction of a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance is useful during the creation of strongly-typed grammars.</span></span>  
  
